00:13:33.257 --> 00:13:36.289
We talk about the Zoroastrian
faith in other videos.

00:13:36.289 --> 00:13:39.645
And Zarathustra, who
is kind of the prophet

00:13:39.645 --> 00:13:41.037
of the Zoroastrian faith,

00:13:41.037 --> 00:13:43.369
he lived someplace between 1500 BCE

00:13:43.369 --> 00:13:46.033
and might have even lived
shortly right before,

00:13:46.033 --> 00:13:47.886
almost near the time of Cyrus the Great.

00:13:47.886 --> 00:13:49.605
But it was really Cyrus
the Great who helps

00:13:49.605 --> 00:13:52.272
